      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, it just feels like everyone is too busy anyway. the people i 'interact' with are just avatars on a screen or voices in an earbud. if i just... stopped. if i wasn't there tomorrow. it wouldn't even be a tragedy, it would just be a quiet silence. nobody would even notice the gap.",
